div.div:
process_file(self) -> ChargepolFigure
With the file determined, we can now process the hdf5 file to a chargepol file. If it was already a chargepol file we can simply start creating a new Chargepol Figure.
At the end of the process we should be able to return a ChargepolFigure class instance.

div.div:
Chargepol.py (Edited)
For .hdf5 files we use an edited version of chargepol. This new version creates a pandas dataframe where all of the data from Chargepol is stored instead of a .csv file.
After all of the data is processed, it the pandas dataframe will be returned.
